<li>6/11/92 <a href="/heritage/library/categories/regulation/bg900.html">Regulatory Relief or Power Grab: Should Congress Expand FDA's Enforcement Authority?</a> by Paul H. Rubin.  (Backgrounder #900)
<li>4/10/92 <a href="/heritage/library/categories/regulation/bgup177.html">Deregulating the Housing Market: What Can Congress Do</a> by Carl F. Horowitz, Ph.D. (Backgrounder Update No. 177)



