<li>4/3/92 <a href="http://www.townhall.com/heritage/library/categories/theory/ib173.html">The Private Property Rights Act: Forcing Federal Regulators To Obey the Bill of Rights</a> by William G. Laffer III. (Issues Bulletin No. 173)


<li>7/15/91 <a href="/heritage/library/categories/regulation/em304.html">Muzzling OIRA: An Attempt to Thwart Bush's War on Regulation</a> by William G. Laffer III. (Executive Memorandum #304)
<li>4/1/91 <a href="/heritage/library/categories/regulation/em299.html">Congress vs. Minorities: The New Davis-Bacon Rules</a> by Scott A. Hodge and Andrew J. Cowin.  (Executive Memorandum #299)
